headline: Marsh McLennan Declares Quarterly Cash Dividend
summary: NEW YORK, September 17, 2025--The Board of Directors of Marsh McLennan (NYSE: MMC) today declared a quarterly dividend of $0.900 per share on outstanding common stock, payable on November 14, 2025, to stockholders of record on October 2, 2025.

headline: BRO Stock Trading at a Discount to Industry at 19.69X: Time to Hold?
summary: Brown & Brown stock remains poised to gain from new business, solid retention, higher core commissions and fees, strategic buyouts and prudent capital deployment.
